EN: A beautiful park was built on the flat ground.
ZH: 这里的平地非常宽敞，适合放牧。
EN: The flat ground here is very spacious and suitable for grazing.
ZH: 这片平地上有许多果树。
EN: There are many fruit trees on this flat ground.
ZH: 在附近的平地上，我们可以看到美丽的日落。
EN: On the nearby flat ground, we can see beautiful sunsets.
ZH: 雨季过后，平地上形成了一个湖泊。
EN: After the rainy season, a lake formed on the flat ground.
ZH: 平地上的土壤非常肥沃。
EN: The soil on the flat ground is very fertile.
ZH: 这片平地被用来建造了一个大型工厂。
EN: This flat ground was used to build a large factory.
ZH: 平地上的夜晚非常安静。
EN: The nights on the flat ground are very quiet.
