EN: There is a small forest on this flat ground.
ZH: 平地上有许多河流流过。
EN: There are many rivers flowing through the flat ground.
ZH: 平地上有一片开满鲜花的草地。
EN: There is a meadow full of flowers on the flat ground.
ZH: 平地上的行人很多，交通繁忙。
EN: There are many pedestrians on the flat ground, and the traffic is busy.
ZH: 这个城市的平地正在被开发为新的住宅区。
EN: The flat ground of this city is being developed into a new residential area.
ZH: 平地上堆积了许多石头。
EN: Many stones are piled up on the flat ground.
